<h2>LifeSkills</h2><p class="eventtime">Every Sunday, from 09/02/2012 to 09/23/2012<span class='event-sep'>, </span><span class="eventTime"> 9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</span></p><br/><b>Group:</b> Life Learning</p><p><b>Coordinator:</b> Life Learning @ PCC</p><!-- Life Learning @ PCC --><div id="text"><h4><b>Our LifeSkills class is a community of adults in all ages and stages of life. We welcome you and ask that you join us on an amazing journey of discovery as we go through different series all year long. &nbsp;</b></h4>
<p><b><br /></b></p>
<h3>Real Characters with real struggles, triumphs, and lives transformed by God' grace.&nbsp;</h3>
<p><a href="/ministries/life-learning/summer/">Check Out Other Classes We Offer</a></p>
<h5><strong>DATES AND TIMES</strong>: Sundays, July 1 - Sept. 2 at 9:00 a.m.&nbsp;<br />LOCATION: gymnasium&nbsp;<br />COST: This class has no cost.&nbsp;<br />*Drop in at anytime during our series. Each lesson is self-contained. &nbsp;</h5>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Real Characters? That's for sure! Joseph, Abraham, Jacob, David, Luke, Timothy, Solomon, Samson, Jonathan are not just Bible Characters they're real people with real issues like ANGER, PRIDE, SELF CENTEREDNESS, DECEIT, ENVY, LUST, GREED, SLOTH, RESENTMENT. We will take a look at their lives and how they dealt with, overcame, and sometimes failed, in the sins we all seem to wrestle with at one time or another. This series, based on the results of a new online Spiritual Growth Tool gets down to the nitty gritty of living under the transforming power of Jesus. Sundays at 9 AM in the Choir Room.</p></div>